 detail-desc\">\n<div class=\"content-fck\">\n<div class=\"content-fck-font-size\">\n<p class=\"fontd fw600 justify\">T\u1eeb t\u1edd m\u1edd s\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00eam khuya nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m m\u1edbi Gi\u00e1p Th\u00ecn 2024, h\u00e0ng ng\u00e0n \u00f4t\u00f4 n\u1ed1i \u0111u\u00f4i nhau \u0111\u1ebfn Khu Du l\u1ecbch V\u0103n h\u00f3a t\u00e2m linh B\u00e0 Ch\u00faa X\u1ee9 &#8211; C\u00e1p treo n\u00fai Sam \u0111i \u0111\u1ea3nh l\u1ec5 B\u00e0<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div id=\"newscontents\" class=\"col-xs-12\">\n<div class=\"content-fck slider-jsgallery\">\n<div class=\"content-fck-font-size\">\n<div class=\"b-img-slider-jsgallery\" data-pos=\"0\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"zoomimg zoomimg2 i-img-slider-jsgallery\" title=\"C\u00e1p treo n\u00fai Sam ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0nh h\u01b0\u01a1ng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u00eam\" src=\"https:\/\/images.baoangiang.com.vn\/image\/fckeditor\/upload\/2024\/20240213\/images\/1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-socail-link=\"https:\/\/baoangiang.com.vn\/cap-treo-nui-sam-phuc-vu-khach-hanh-huong-xuyen-dem-a387993.html\" data-pos=\"0\"><\/div>\n<div class=\"b-img-slider-jsgallery\" data-pos=\"1\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"zoomimg zoomimg2 i-img-slider-jsgallery\" title=\"C\u00e1p treo n\u00fai Sam ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0nh h\u01b0\u01a1ng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u00eam\" src=\"https:\/\/images.baoangiang.com.vn\/image\/fckeditor\/upload\/2024\/20240213\/images\/2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-socail-link=\"https:\/\/baoangiang.com.vn\/cap-treo-nui-sam-phuc-vu-khach-hanh-huong-xuyen-dem-a387993.html\" data-pos=\"1\"><\/div>\n<div class=\"b-img-slider-jsgallery\" data-pos=\"2\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"zoomimg zoomimg2 i-img-slider-jsgallery\" title=\"C\u00e1p treo n\u00fai Sam ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0nh h\u01b0\u01a1ng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u00eam\" src=\"https:\/\/images.baoangiang.com.vn\/image\/fckeditor\/upload\/2024\/20240213\/images\/3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-socail-link=\"https:\/\/baoangiang.com.vn\/cap-treo-nui-sam-phuc-vu-khach-hanh-huong-xuyen-dem-a387993.html\" data-pos=\"2\"><\/div>\n<p class=\"note ignore\">Nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m m\u1edbi, r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00f4ng du kh\u00e1ch \u0111i \u0111\u1ea3nh l\u1ec5 B\u00e0 Ch\u00faa X\u1ee9 n\u00fai Sam \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u kh\u1ea5n cho m\u1ed9t n\u0103m 2024 b\u00ecnh an, thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i, l\u00e0m \u0103n ph\u00e1t \u0111\u1ea1t<\/p>\n<p>V\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u1eafc \u0111\u1ecba \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n Mi\u1ebfu B\u00e0 Ch\u00faa X\u1ee9 n\u00fai Sam, khu\u00f4n vi\u00ean r\u1ed9ng l\u1edbn 10ha, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng b\u00e0i b\u1ea3n, v\u1edbi b\u00e3i gi\u1eef \u00f4t\u00f4 c\u00f3 s\u1ee9c ch\u1ee9a l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u00ean 2.000 xe, c\u00f9ng 4 s\u1ea3nh nh\u00e0 h\u00e0ng k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p c\u00f4ng vi\u00ean r\u1ed9ng r\u00e3i, tho\u00e1ng m\u00e1t, ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 24\/24\u2026, C\u00e1p treo n\u00fai Sam mang \u0111\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u ti\u1ec7n \u00edch h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ebfn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ecf qua khi \u0111\u1ebfn\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/baoangiang.com.vn\/trong-tinh\/tp-chau-doc\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">TP. Ch\u00e2u \u0110\u1ed1c<\/a>\u00a0v\u00e0o d\u1ecbp l\u1ec5 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m.<\/p>\n<div class=\"b-img-slider-jsgallery\" data-pos=\"3\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"zoomimg zoomimg2 i-img-slider-jsgallery\" title=\"C\u00e1p treo n\u00fai Sam ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0nh h\u01b0\u01a1ng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u00eam\" src=\"https:\/\/images.baoangiang.com.vn\/image\/fckeditor\/upload\/2024\/20240213\/images\/4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-socail-link=\"https:\/\/baoangiang.com.vn\/cap-treo-nui-sam-phuc-vu-khach-hanh-huong-xuyen-dem-a387993.html\" data-pos=\"3\"><\/div>\n<div class=\"b-img-slider-jsgallery\" data-pos=\"4\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"zoomimg zoomimg2 i-img-slider-jsgallery\" title=\"C\u00e1p treo n\u00fai Sam ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0nh h\u01b0\u01a1ng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u00eam\" src=\"https:\/\/images.baoangiang.com.vn\/image\/fckeditor\/upload\/2024\/20240213\/images\/4_1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-socail-link=\"https:\/\/baoangiang.com.vn\/cap-treo-nui-sam-phuc-vu-khach-hanh-huong-xuyen-dem-a387993.html\" data-pos=\"4\"><\/div>\n<p class=\"note ignore\">R\u1ea5t \u0111\u00f4ng du kh\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi C\u00e1p treo n\u00fai Sam t\u1eeb t\u1edd m\u1edd s\u00e1ng cho \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00eam khuya<\/p>\n<p>Khu Du l\u1ecbch V\u0103n h\u00f3a t\u00e2m linh B\u00e0 Ch\u00faa X\u1ee9 &#8211; C\u00e1p treo n\u00fai Sam (C\u00e1p treo n\u00fai Sam) \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 ti\u1ec7n \u00edch \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 chu \u0111\u00e1o cho du kh\u00e1ch \u0111i \u0111\u1ea3nh l\u1ec5 B\u00e0 Ch\u00faa X\u1ee9 n\u00fai Sam d\u00f9 l\u00e0 ng\u00e0y hay \u0111\u00eam, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u00e3i nghi\u1ec7m tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n chuy\u1ebfn du l\u1ecbch t\u00e2m linh khi \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi n\u01a1i \u0111\u00e2y.<\/p>\n<div class=\"b-img-slider-jsgallery\" data-pos=\"5\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"zoomimg zoomimg2 i-img-slider-jsgallery\" title=\"C\u00e1p treo n\u00fai Sam ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0nh h\u01b0\u01a1ng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u00eam\" src=\"https:\/\/images.baoangiang.com.vn\/image\/fckeditor\/upload\/2024\/20240213\/images\/5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-socail-link=\"https:\/\/baoangiang.com.vn\/cap-treo-nui-sam-phuc-vu-khach-hanh-huong-xuyen-dem-a387993.html\" data-pos=\"5\"><\/div>\n<div class=\"b-img-slider-jsgallery\" data-pos=\"6\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"zoomimg zoomimg2 i-img-slider-jsgallery\" title=\"C\u00e1p treo n\u00fai Sam ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0nh h\u01b0\u01a1ng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u00eam\" src=\"https:\/\/images.baoangiang.com.vn\/image\/fckeditor\/upload\/2024\/20240213\/images\/6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-socail-link=\"https:\/\/baoangiang.com.vn\/cap-treo-nui-sam-phuc-vu-khach-hanh-huong-xuyen-dem-a387993.html\" data-pos=\"6\"><\/div>\n<p class=\"note ignore\">B\u00e3i gi\u1eef \u00f4t\u00f4 c\u00f3 s\u1ee9c ch\u1ee9a l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u00ean 2.000 xe lu\u00f4n t\u1ea5p n\u1eadp<\/p>\n<div class=\"b-img-slider-jsgallery\" data-pos=\"7\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"zoomimg zoomimg2 i-img-slider-jsgallery\" title=\"C\u00e1p treo n\u00fai Sam ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0nh h\u01b0\u01a1ng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u00eam\" src=\"https:\/\/images.baoangiang.com.vn\/image\/fckeditor\/upload\/2024\/20240213\/images\/7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-socail-link=\"https:\/\/baoangiang.com.vn\/cap-treo-nui-sam-phuc-vu-khach-hanh-huong-xuyen-dem-a387993.html\" data-pos=\"7\"><\/div>\n<div class=\"b-img-slider-jsgallery\" data-pos=\"8\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"zoomimg zoomimg2 i-img-slider-jsgallery\" title=\"C\u00e1p treo n\u00fai Sam ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0nh h\u01b0\u01a1ng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u00eam\" src=\"https:\/\/images.baoangiang.com.vn\/image\/fckeditor\/upload\/2024\/20240213\/images\/8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-socail-link=\"https:\/\/baoangiang.com.vn\/cap-treo-nui-sam-phuc-vu-khach-hanh-huong-xuyen-dem-a387993.html\" data-pos=\"8\"><\/div>\n<p class=\"note ignore\">Du kh\u00e1ch x\u1ebfp h\u00e0ng ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean c\u00e1p treo<\/p>\n<div class=\"b-img-slider-jsgallery\" data-pos=\"9\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"zoomimg zoomimg2 i-img-slider-jsgallery\" title=\"C\u00e1p treo n\u00fai Sam ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0nh h\u01b0\u01a1ng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u00eam\" src=\"https:\/\/images.baoangiang.com.vn\/image\/fckeditor\/upload\/2024\/20240213\/images\/9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-socail-link=\"https:\/\/baoangiang.com.vn\/cap-treo-nui-sam-phuc-vu-khach-hanh-huong-xuyen-dem-a387993.html\" data-pos=\"9\"><\/div>\n<p>Khu du l\u1ecbch t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 \u0103n u\u1ed1ng 24\/7, v\u1edbi cung c\u00e1ch ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 chu \u0111\u00e1o, \u00e2n c\u1ea7n, chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p, c\u00f9ng nh\u1eefng m\u00f3n \u0103n \u0111\u1eb7c s\u1ea3n th\u01a1m ngon, n\u00f3ng h\u1ed5i lu\u00f4n s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng nhu c\u1ea7u du kh\u00e1ch.<\/p>\n<p>\u0110\u1ebfn v\u1edbi C\u00e1p treo n\u00fai Sam, b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u00eam ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng v\u1ebb \u0111\u1eb9p b\u1edfi c\u1ea3nh s\u1eafc thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean, ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1o m\u00e0 c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng y\u00ean b\u00ecnh khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eafm m\u00ecnh trong kh\u00f4ng gian Ph\u1eadt gi\u00e1o.<\/p>\n<p>Ban ng\u00e0y ng\u1eafm c\u1ea3nh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1eb9p l\u00e0 th\u1ebf, nh\u01b0ng khi v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00eam c\u00f2n lung linh h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n. Ng\u1ed3i c\u00e1p treo, du kh\u00e1ch c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 bao qu\u00e1t to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 TP. Ch\u00e2u \u0110\u1ed1c, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng bi\u00ean gi\u1edbi Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u2013 Campuchia. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, khi \u0111i c\u00e1p treo bu\u1ed5i t\u1ed1i, trong kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed h\u01a1i se l\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a mi\u1ec1n vi\u1ec5n bi\u00ean, to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 TP. Ch\u00e2u \u0110\u1ed1c v\u1edbi \u00e1nh \u0111\u00e8n lung linh v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00eam s\u1ebd \u0111em l\u1ea1i cho du kh\u00e1ch tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi \u1edf m\u1ecdi g\u00f3c nh\u00ecn.<\/p>\n<div class=\"b-img-slider-jsgallery\" data-pos=\"10\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"zoomimg zoomimg2 i-img-slider-jsgallery\" title=\"C\u00e1p treo n\u00fai Sam ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0nh h\u01b0\u01a1ng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u00eam\" src=\"https:\/\/images.baoangiang.com.vn\/image\/fckeditor\/upload\/2024\/20240213\/images\/10.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-socail-link=\"https:\/\/baoangiang.com.vn\/cap-treo-nui-sam-phuc-vu-khach-hanh-huong-xuyen-dem-a387993.html\" data-pos=\"10\"><\/div>\n<div class=\"b-img-slider-jsgallery\" data-pos=\"11\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"zoomimg zoomimg2 i-img-slider-jsgallery\" title=\"C\u00e1p treo n\u00fai Sam ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0nh h\u01b0\u01a1ng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u00eam\" src=\"https:\/\/images.baoangiang.com.vn\/image\/fckeditor\/upload\/2024\/20240213\/images\/11.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-socail-link=\"https:\/\/baoangiang.com.vn\/cap-treo-nui-sam-phuc-vu-khach-hanh-huong-xuyen-dem-a387993.html\" data-pos=\"11\"><\/div>\n<p>Ban Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c C\u00e1p treo n\u00fai Sam \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng gi\u00e1 v\u00e9 c\u00e1p treo \u01b0u \u0111\u00e3i nh\u1ea5t cho l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u00e1n b\u1ed9, c\u00f4ng nh\u00e2n, vi\u00ean ch\u1ee9c v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi lao \u0111\u1ed9ng (xu\u1ea5t tr\u00ecnh th\u1ebb c\u00f4ng nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean ho\u1eb7c c\u00f3 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn n\u01a1i l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c) v\u00e0 b\u00e0 con h\u00e0nh h\u01b0\u01a1ng (xe 16 ch\u1ed7 tr\u1edf l\u00ean), v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 v\u00e9 c\u00e1p treo ch\u1ec9 79.000 \u0111\u1ed3ng\/ng\u01b0\u1eddi, t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 9\/2 \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ebft\u00a0 9\/3. \u0110\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi, s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c tri\u1ec3n khai nhi\u1ec1u ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh \u01b0u \u0111\u00e3i kh\u00e1c k\u00e9o d\u00e0i \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ebft l\u1ec5 V\u00eda B\u00e0 n\u0103m nay.<\/p>\n<div class=\"b-img-slider-jsgallery\" data-pos=\"12\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"zoomimg zoomimg2 i-img-slider-jsgallery\" title=\"C\u00e1p treo n\u00fai Sam ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0nh h\u01b0\u01a1ng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u00eam\" src=\"https:\/\/images.baoangiang.com.vn\/image\/fckeditor\/upload\/2024\/20240213\/images\/12.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-socail-link=\"https:\/\/baoangiang.com.vn\/cap-treo-nui-sam-phuc-vu-khach-hanh-huong-xuyen-dem-a387993.html\" data-pos=\"12\"><\/div>\n<p class=\"note ignore\">\u0110\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea3o ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n, c\u00e1n b\u1ed9, c\u00f4ng nh\u00e2n, vi\u00ean ch\u1ee9c, ng\u01b0\u1eddi lao \u0111\u1ed9ng ph\u1ea5n kh\u1edfi, tranh th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2y tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn \u01b0u \u0111\u00e3i<\/p>\n<p>\u0110\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi, C\u00e1p treo n\u00fai Sam tri\u1ec3n khai Cu\u1ed9c thi thi \u201cCheck-in ngay &#8211; Nh\u1eadn qu\u00e0 li\u1ec1n tay\u201d cho du kh\u00e1ch, v\u1edbi qu\u00e0 t\u1eb7ng ngay 3 v\u00e9 c\u00e1p treo cho du kh\u00e1ch check-in, chia s\u1ebd tr\u00ean c\u00e1c m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i, nh\u01b0: Facebook, Tiktok&#8230;, c\u00f9ng nhi\u1ec1u ph\u1ea7n th\u01b0\u1edfng h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn kh\u00e1c cho nh\u1eefng kh\u00e1ch c\u00f3 l\u01b0\u1ee3t theo d\u00f5i, b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn cao theo t\u1eeb 200 l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1edf l\u00ean.<\/p>\n<div class=\"b-img-slider-jsgallery\" data-pos=\"13\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"zoomimg zoomimg2 i-img-slider-jsgallery\" title=\"C\u00e1p treo n\u00fai Sam ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0nh h\u01b0\u01a1ng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u00eam\" src=\"https:\/\/images.baoangiang.com.vn\/image\/fckeditor\/upload\/2024\/20240213\/images\/14.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-socail-link=\"https:\/\/baoangiang.com.vn\/cap-treo-nui-sam-phuc-vu-khach-hanh-huong-xuyen-dem-a387993.html\" data-pos=\"13\"><\/div>\n<p>Ca s\u1ef9 Qu\u00e1ch Tu\u1ea5n Du chia s\u1ebb: \u201cVi\u1ebfng B\u00e0 Ch\u00faa X\u1ee9, \u0111i c\u00e1p treo l\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh n\u00fai Sam \u0111\u1ea3nh l\u1ec5 b\u1ec7 B\u00e0 v\u1eeba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh t\u00e2m linh, v\u1eeba tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i, nhanh ch\u00f3ng, ti\u1ec7n l\u1ee3i v\u00e0 c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 c\u1ea3nh quan h\u00f9ng v\u0129, lung linh t\u1eeb tr\u00ean cao\u201d.<\/p>\n<div class=\"b-img-slider-jsgallery\" data-pos=\"14\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"zoomimg zoomimg2 i-img-slider-jsgallery\" title=\"C\u00e1p treo n\u00fai Sam ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0nh h\u01b0\u01a1ng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u00eam\" src=\"https:\/\/images.baoangiang.com.vn\/image\/fckeditor\/upload\/2024\/20240213\/images\/15.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-socail-link=\"https:\/\/baoangiang.com.vn\/cap-treo-nui-sam-phuc-vu-khach-hanh-huong-xuyen-dem-a387993.html\" data-pos=\"14\"><\/div>\n<div class=\"b-img-slider-jsgallery\" data-pos=\"15\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"zoomimg zoomimg2 i-img-slider-jsgallery\" title=\"C\u00e1p treo n\u00fai Sam ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0nh h\u01b0\u01a1ng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u00eam\" src=\"https:\/\/images.baoangiang.com.vn\/image\/fckeditor\/upload\/2024\/20240213\/images\/16.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-socail-link=\"https:\/\/baoangiang.com.vn\/cap-treo-nui-sam-phuc-vu-khach-hanh-huong-xuyen-dem-a387993.html\" data-pos=\"15\"><\/div>\n<p>Di\u1ec5n vi\u00ean Tuy\u1ec1n m\u1eadp chia s\u1ebb: &#8220;Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y, khi \u0111\u1ea3nh l\u1ec5 B\u00e0 Ch\u00faa X\u1ee9 xong ch\u1ec9 nhanh nhanh mong quay v\u1ec1, do th\u1eddi gian \u0111i v\u1ec1 m\u1ea5t r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian tr\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi 16 -18 ti\u1ebfng, \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng xa k\u1eb9t xe r\u1ea5t m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi. V\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u anh ch\u1ecb em ngh\u1ec7 s\u1ef9 truy\u1ec1n tai cho bi\u1ebft chuy\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh h\u01b0\u01a1ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n khi \u0111i c\u00e1p treo l\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh n\u00fai Sam h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh vi\u1ebfng b\u1ec7 B\u00e0 Ch\u00faa X\u1ee9, chi\u00eam b\u00e1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng Ph\u1eadt ng\u1ecdc song sinh v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn l\u1ed9c V\u00eda B\u00e0 &#8211;\u00a0 t\u00fai c\u00e1t nh\u1ecf d\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1eb7t b\u00e1t nhang, do Ban Qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd khu du l\u1ecbch t\u1eadn t\u00e2m chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb\u2026<\/p>\n<p>Sau chuy\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh h\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u1edf v\u1ec1, Tuy\u1ec1n m\u1eadp c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y th\u00e2n t\u00e2m r\u1ea5t an l\u1ea1c, th\u01b0 th\u00e1i, c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u mong \u01b0\u1edbc thi\u1ec7n l\u00e0nh, hy v\u1ecdng cho m\u1ed9t n\u0103m m\u1edbi b\u00ecnh an. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, \u0111i c\u00e1p treo n\u00fai Sam r\u1ea5t ti\u1ec7n l\u1ee3i, m\u1eb7c \u00e1o d\u00e0i c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y v\u01b0\u1edbng v\u00edu v\u00ec cabin r\u1ea5t r\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 tho\u00e1ng \u0111\u00e3ng&#8221;.<\/p>\n<p>Ngo\u00e0i ra, ca s\u1ef9 Qu\u00e1ch Tu\u1ea5n Du &#8211; \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u C\u00e1p treo n\u00fai Sam v\u00e0 di\u1ec5n vi\u00ean Tuy\u1ec1n m\u1eadp c\u00f2n g\u1eedi t\u1eb7ng tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng ch\u1ee5c ng\u00e0n v\u00e9 m\u1eddi \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00f4ng nh\u00e2n c\u00e1c khu c\u00f4ng nghi\u1ec7p v\u00e0 b\u00e0 con h\u00e0nh h\u01b0\u01a1ng.<\/p>\n<div class=\"b-img-slider-jsgallery\" data-pos=\"16\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"zoomimg zoomimg2 i-img-slider-jsgallery\" title=\"C\u00e1p treo n\u00fai Sam ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0nh h\u01b0\u01a1ng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u00eam\" src=\"https:\/\/images.baoangiang.com.vn\/image\/fckeditor\/upload\/2024\/20240213\/images\/17.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-socail-link=\"https:\/\/baoangiang.com.vn\/cap-treo-nui-sam-phuc-vu-khach-hanh-huong-xuyen-dem-a387993.html\" data-pos=\"16\"><\/div>\n<div class=\"b-img-slider-jsgallery\" data-pos=\"17\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"zoomimg zoomimg2 i-img-slider-jsgallery\" title=\"C\u00e1p treo n\u00fai Sam ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0nh h\u01b0\u01a1ng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u00eam\" src=\"https:\/\/images.baoangiang.com.vn\/image\/fckeditor\/upload\/2024\/20240213\/images\/18.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-socail-link=\"https:\/\/baoangiang.com.vn\/cap-treo-nui-sam-phuc-vu-khach-hanh-huong-xuyen-dem-a387993.html\" data-pos=\"17\"><\/div>\n<p class=\"note ignore\">Ch\u00f9a &#8220;M\u1ed9t C\u1ed9t&#8221; t\u1ea1i khu du l\u1ecbch<\/p>\n<div class=\"b-img-slider-jsgallery\" data-pos=\"18\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"zoomimg zoomimg2 i-img-slider-jsgallery\" title=\"C\u00e1p treo n\u00fai Sam ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0nh h\u01b0\u01a1ng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u00eam\